metadata.name: FakeDOSSoulz #1/104
metadata.description:
First reward token for OG minters and holders of FakeDOSPepez.

You are the Soulz of FakeDOSPepez.

Claiming this token makes you an OG FakeDOSPepez supporter, and as long as you hold it you'll be cozy.

Thanks for your support and love for FakeDOSPepez.
